到班畜生拎到<br />\n即時又扮愛国 話做中国狗最好<br />\n要其他人繼續做隻中国狗要愛国<br />\n所以話中国支那賤畜蝗蟲真係幾撚恐怖<br />\n無人格無人性唯利是圖<br />\n玩個人崇拜 當個小熊維尼係皇帝<br />\n做哂太監宮女爭住奶<br />\n丫，我唔記得左<br />\n中国係最無骨氣既地方，打亂種<br />\n滿漢明清乜撚族都有<br />\n不過呢 都係中国狗，何必分那麼細<br />\n<br />\n一句 中国又贏呀！"},{"pid":"49561c0d7f55c7e58ee5d1e3feb3c0eabeb84703","tid":1037662,"uid":57023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cefd73b09823c0cc46fa5b5869c1acb4b85b823b","tid":1037662,"uid":83344,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"條片入面出聲既全部講廣東話，又冇鄉音。正常呢D政府片一定搵齊晒鬼佬中東佬菲傭同中國佬蝗。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:43:01.000Z","msg":"奴才港苦點敢得罪d蝗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又怕種族歧視/人權棍嘈, 只識自我矮化天天打擊港人自尊心就會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa848f3fe9cdebb83e466a9f51bf36da3a5ba955","tid":1037662,"uid":59678,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11721d5c631fc78ca5773beffc64f3c9d2910e43","tid":1037662,"uid":209029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T09:57:46.000Z","msg":"開Speaker真係好冇文化。"},{"pid":"55f87f6afc8a59f26f9bbf4e94e3725396eb06e0","tid":1037662,"uid":45148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"政府每日派150個生番<br />\n今曰政府叫你要禮讓<br />\n港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f461bd614176ace57e084bcac4e5ce5fe64c8e90","tid":1037662,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97f7b6495832309b8e4be67031b976f74e59f89d","tid":1037662,"uid":202698,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T06:04:38.000Z","msg":"廣告片整到Deanie姐有D惡，基本上都係不斷鬧人式教育自私乘客<br />\n係咪反映緊香港人已經唔鬧唔得??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:02:08.000Z","msg":"運輸署帶頭鼓吹香港人要勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b18d522babbbd1cc98f9485730db